    "en": {
      "title": "An old man died of corona infection in Yali",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna. A 91-year-old man from Vadamaratsi area was admitted to Barudhiturai Aadar Hospital on the 21st due to illness.",
        "In this case, he was confirmed to be infected with corona and died last Saturday without treatment.",
        "It is noteworthy that the rate of spread of corona infection is increasing day by day and corona deaths are also being reported.",
        "It was mentioned in the statement issued by the Ministry of Health yesterday that 3 Covid deaths were reported the day before yesterday."
      ],
